\"2015-08-15 00:00:00 UTC\",\"Kate Schell\",\"kschell214@gmail.com\",\"\",\"Juicing Box - Regular\",\"29 Boxwood Lane\",\"\",\"New Milford\",\"CT\",\"06776\",\"1\",\"1\",\"N/A\",\"\",\"true\",\"$42.95\",\"$0.00\",\"$42.95\",\"shipped\",\"\"\n","markerStore":{"nextMarkerId":2,"markersById":{"0":{"range":{"start":{"row":0,"column":0},"end":{"row":0,"column":0}},"properties":{"type":"selection","editorId":566,"preserveFolds":true,"goalScreenRange":null},"reversed":false,"tailed":false,"valid":true,"invalidate":"never","maintainHistory":true}},"version":2},"history":{"version":3,"nextCheckpointId":0,"undoStack":[],"redoStack":[]},"encoding":"utf8","filePath":"/Users/joegesualdo/Downloads/subscription_shipments (50).csv","digestWhenLastPersisted":"da39a3ee5e6b4b0d3255bfef95601890afd80709","preferredLineEnding":null,"deserializer":"TextBuffer","version":2},{"load":false,"text":"1\r\n00:00:16,200 --> 00:00:17,634\r\nHey, what are you doing?\r\n\r\n2\r\n00:00:21,880 --> 00:00:24,520\r\nJesus.\r\nDid you get\r\na good look?\r\n\r\n3\r\n00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:26,671\r\nBlue Toyota Camry,\r\nthat's all I saw.\r\n\r\n4\r\n00:00:26,760 --> 00:00:28,080\r\nIt's the Wartons' dog.\r\n\r\n5\r\n00:00:28,200 --> 00:00:29,475\r\nOh, man.\r\n\r\n6\r\n00:00:29,560 --> 00:00:30,880\r\nIt's not gonna make it.\r\n\r\n7\r\n00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:32,030\r\nGo see if they're home.\r\n\r\n8\r\n00:00:44,360 --> 00:00:45,714\r\nIt's okay.\r\n\r\n9\r\n00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:51,151\r\nThere are two kinds of pain.\r\n\r\n10\r\n00:00:51,280 --> 00:00:53,272\r\nThe sort of pain\r\nthat makes you strong\r\n\r\n11\r\n00:00:53,360 --> 00:00:57,240\r\nor useless pain,\r\nthe sort of pain\r\nthat's only suffering.\r\n\r\n12\r\n00:00:58,680 --> 00:01:01,320\r\nI have no patience\r\nfor useless things.\r\n\r\n13\r\n00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:06,517\r\nMoments like\r\nthis require someone\r\nwho will act.\r\n\r\n14\r\n00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:09,638\r\nWho will do\r\nthe unpleasant thing,\r\n\r\n15\r\n00:01:09,720 --> 00:01:11,473\r\nthe necessary thing.\r\n\r\n16\r\n00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:18,074\r\nThere.\r\n\r\n17\r\n00:01:18,160 --> 00:01:19,640\r\nNo more pain.\r\n\r\n18\r\n00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:24,600\r\nIt was\r\na hit and run.\r\nI'm awfully sorry.\r\n\r\n19\r\n00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:26,911\r\nHe must've jumped\r\nover the fence again.\r\n\r\n20\r\n00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:30,198\r\nLook, Steve is gonna\r\nfile a report on the car.\r\nHe'll put his people on it.\r\n\r\n21\r\n00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:32,158\r\nWe'll track them down.\r\n\r\n22\r\n00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:53,714\r\nStunning.\r\n\r\n23\r\n00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,270\r\nShall we?\r\n\r\n24\r\n00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:57,317\r\n<i>Three, two, one.</i>\r\n\r\n25\r\n00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:59,710\r\nHappy New Year!\r\n\r\n26\r\n00:02:06,080 --> 00:02:07,070\r\nOh.\r\n\r\n27\r\n00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:08,674\r\nPresident-elect\r\nGarrett Walker.\r\n\r\n28\r\n00:02:09,040 --> 00:02:10,269\r\nDo I like him? No.\r\n\r\n29\r\n00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:12,471\r\nDo I believe in him?\r\nThat's beside the point.\r\n\r\n30\r\n00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:14,677\r\nAny politician that\r\ngets 70 million votes\r\n\r\n31\r\n00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:16,717\r\nhas tapped into\r\nsomething larger\r\nthan himself,\r\n\r\n32\r\n00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:19,110\r\nlarger than even me,\r\nas much as I hate to admit it.\r\n\r\n33\r\n00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:22,039\r\nLook at that winning smile,\r\nthose trusting eyes.\r\n\r\n34\r\n00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:24,880\r\nI latched onto him early on\r\nand made myself vital.\r\n\r\n35\r\n00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:29,193\r\nAfter 22 years in Congress,\r\nI can smell which way\r\nthe wind is blowing.\r\n\r\n36\r\n00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:32,430\r\nJim Matthews, his Right\r\nHonorable Vice President.\r\n\r\n37\r\n00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:34,079\r\nFormer governor\r\nof Pennsylvania.\r\n\r\n38\r\n00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:37,598\r\nHe did his duty in\r\ndelivering the Keystone\r\nState, bless his heart.\r\n\r\n39\r\n00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:39,672\r\nNow they're about to\r\nput him out to pasture.\r\n\r\n40\r\n00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:42,150\r\nBut he looks\r\nhappy enough,\r\ndoesn't he?\r\n\r\n41\r\n00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:45,551\r\nFor some, it's simply\r\nthe size of the chair.\r\n\r\n42\r\n00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:51,590\r\nLinda Vasquez,\r\nWalker's chief of staff.\r\nI got her hired.\r\n\r\n43\r\n00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:55,390\r\nShe's a woman, check.\r\nAnd a Latina, check.\r\nBut more important than that,\r\n\r\n44\r\n00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:59,276\r\nshe's as tough as\r\na two-dollar steak.\r\nCheck, check, check.\r\n\r\n45\r\n00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,680\r\nWhen it comes to\r\nthe White House,\r\n\r\n46\r\n00:03:00,760 --> 00:03:02,717\r\nyou not\r\nonly need the keys\r\nin your back-pocket,\r\n\r\n47\r\n00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,439\r\nyou need the gatekeeper.\r\n\r\n48\r\n00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:07,240\r\nAs for me,\r\nI'm just the lowly\r\nHouse Majority Whip.\r\n\r\n49\r\n00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:09,152\r\nI keep things\r\nmoving in a Congress\r\n\r\n50\r\n00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:11,112\r\nchoked by\r\npettiness and lassitude.\r\n\r\n51\r\n00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:14,557\r\nMy job is to clear the pipes\r\nand keep the sludge moving.\r\n\r\n52\r\n00:03:14,640 --> 00:03:16,279\r\nBut I won't have to be\r\na plumber much longer.\r\n\r\n53\r\n00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:19,353\r\nI've done my time.\r\nI've backed the right man.\r\n\r\n54\r\n00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:23,520\r\nGive and take.\r\n\r\n55\r\n00:03:23,640 --> 00:03:25,438\r\nWelcome to Washington.\r\n\r\n56\r\n00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,639\r\nYou need a haircut.\r\n\r\n57\r\n00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:07,040\r\nYou think?\r\n\r\n58\r\n00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,640\r\nA little trim.\r\n\r\n59\r\n00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:12,234\r\nWhat are you going to wear?\r\n\r\n60\r\n00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:14,161\r\nYou mean for\r\nthe meeting?\r\nFor the announcement.\r\n\r\n61\r\n00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:17,114\r\nI'll wear my navy blue,\r\nthe one with the pinstripes.\r\n\r\n62\r\n00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:20,113\r\nGood. You look\r\nhandsome in that suit.\r\n\r\n63\r\n00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:24,310\r\nI don't know if\r\nthey'll announce\r\nbefore your board meeting.\r\n\r\n64\r\n00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,473\r\nAs long as I can say\r\nthe donation is coming.\r\n\r\n65\r\n00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:29,997\r\nSoon as it's official,\r\nSanCorp will\r\nwrite you a check.\r\n\r\n66\r\n00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:36,155\r\nThis is going to be\r\na big year for us.\r\n\r\n67\r\n00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,640\r\nThey're gonna want\r\nto start with something big.\r\n\r\n68\r\n00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:58,274\r\nThat's why I'm here\r\n\r\n69\r\n00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,680\r\nReally? What?\r\n\r\n70\r\n00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:02,195\r\nI'd say immigration,\r\nbanking or education.\r\n\r\n71\r\n00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:04,192\r\nBut none of my regular\r\nsources can confirm that.\r\n\r\n72\r\n00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:07,352\r\nBecause they don't\r\nknow, or because\r\nthey're not talking?\r\n\r\n73\r\n00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,596\r\nBecause they don't know.\r\n\r\n74\r\n00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:10,439\r\nKeep at it.\r\nGet me something.\r\n\r\n75\r\n00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:15,392\r\nSorry. Sorry,\r\nMr. Hammerschmidt. Zoe.\r\n\r\n76\r\n00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,679\r\nBarnes.\r\nRight.\r\n\r\n77\r\n00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:24,240\r\nDid it take him a year\r\nto remember your name?\r\n\r\n78\r\n00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:25,310\r\nLonger.\r\n\r\n79\r\n00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:27,876\r\nGood morning, Lucas.\r\n\r\n80\r\n00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:30,031\r\nWhat can I do for you, Zoe?\r\n\r\n81\r\n00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,757\r\nI am sick of\r\nthe Fairfax\r\nCounty Council.\r\n\r\n82\r\n00:06:33,840 --> 00:06:34,876\r\nYou tell me every day.\r\n\r\n83\r\n00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:36,394\r\nMove me online.\r\n\r\n84\r\n00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,550\r\nMy own blog.\r\n\r\n85\r\n00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:39,552\r\nFirst person.\r\nSubjective. 500 words.\r\n\r\n86\r\n00: