\n\r\n707\r\n00:45:25,360 --> 00:45:27,875\r\nI'm the Whip.\r\nIt's my job to know.\r\n\r\n708\r\n00:45:27,960 --> 00:45:30,873\r\nLook, they let me off.\r\nThere's no charges.\r\n\r\n709\r\n00:45:30,960 --> 00:45:32,360\r\nIt's all taken care of.\r\n\r\n710\r\n00:45:33,160 --> 00:45:35,629\r\nHonestly, Peter,\r\ndo you really think\r\n\r\n711\r\n00:45:35,800 --> 00:45:38,315\r\nthese things\r\njust take care\r\nof themselves?\r\n\r\n712\r\n00:45:39,160 --> 00:45:40,150\r\nYou...\r\n\r\n713\r\n00:45:43,640 --> 00:45:46,155\r\nIt was just this\r\none time, Frank.\r\nI swear to God.\r\n\r\n714\r\n00:45:46,240 --> 00:45:48,516\r\nThen you must hold\r\nGod in very low esteem,\r\n\r\n715\r\n00:45:48,680 --> 00:45:50,990\r\nbecause we both know\r\nthat's a lie.\r\n\r\n716\r\n00:45:52,160 --> 00:45:54,834\r\nSolicitation,\r\ncontrolled substances,\r\n\r\n717\r\n00:45:54,920 --> 00:45:56,832\r\ndriving under the influence...\r\n\r\n718\r\n00:45:57,520 --> 00:45:59,955\r\nYou've got quite\r\na long list of hobbies.\r\n\r\n719\r\n00:46:01,560 --> 00:46:02,835\r\nWhat is it you want?\r\n\r\n720\r\n00:46:15,080 --> 00:46:19,791\r\nYour absolute,\r\nunquestioning loyalty.\r\n\r\n721\r\n00:46:20,280 --> 00:46:21,270\r\nAlways.\r\n\r\n722\r\n00:46:21,360 --> 00:46:25,400\r\nDo not misunderstand\r\nwhat I mean by loyalty.\r\n\r\n723\r\n00:46:25,480 --> 00:46:28,439\r\nAnything. Name it, Frank.\r\n\r\n724\r\n00:46:28,520 --> 00:46:30,273\r\nYou seem far too relaxed.\r\n\r\n725\r\n00:46:30,360 --> 00:46:31,953\r\nI'm not.\r\n\r\n726\r\n00:46:32,040 --> 00:46:33,759\r\nYou shouldn't be.\r\n\r\n727\r\n00:46:35,960 --> 00:46:37,110\r\nDoug will be in touch.\r\n\r\n728\r\n00:46:42,560 --> 00:46:45,997\r\nHang on. Where\r\nhave you been?\r\nI've been calling you.\r\n\r\n729\r\n00:46:46,080 --> 00:46:47,639\r\nEverybody's\r\nworking double-time\r\non inauguration\r\n\r\n730\r\n00:46:47,720 --> 00:46:49,393\r\nand you just up\r\nand disappear...\r\n\r\n731\r\n00:46:50,240 --> 00:46:51,230\r\nHang on.\r\n\r\n732\r\n00:46:59,520 --> 00:47:00,510\r\nLet me call you back.\r\n\r\n733\r\n00:47:05,600 --> 00:47:07,273\r\nWhere did you get this?\r\nWrong question.\r\n\r\n734\r\n00:47:07,360 --> 00:47:11,149\r\nThe right question is\r\nhow quickly can we\r\nget it up on the site?\r\n\r\n735\r\n00:47:11,240 --> 00:47:12,594\r\nI have to run this past Tom.\r\n\r\n736\r\n00:47:13,880 --> 00:47:16,998\r\nLet's get legal on this,\r\nmake sure we're not\r\nbreaking any laws.\r\n\r\n737\r\n00:47:17,920 --> 00:47:18,910\r\nYou won't tell me your source?\r\n\r\n738\r\n00:47:19,040 --> 00:47:20,076\r\nI can't do that.\r\n\r\n739\r\n00:47:20,120 --> 00:47:22,919\r\nFine. But if legal\r\nfinds even one...\r\nI understand.\r\n\r\n740\r\n00:47:23,000 --> 00:47:24,320\r\nHow long do you\r\nthink that will take?\r\n\r\n741\r\n00:47:24,440 --> 00:47:25,715\r\nWe should get this\r\nonline right away.\r\n\r\n742\r\n00:47:25,800 --> 00:47:27,473\r\nI'm not just\r\ngoing to scan\r\na 300-page document\r\n\r\n743\r\n00:47:27,560 --> 00:47:29,199\r\nand put it up\r\nbefore we've gone\r\nthrough every...\r\n\r\n744\r\n00:47:29,280 --> 00:47:30,430\r\nI did that already.\r\n\r\n745\r\n00:47:31,240 --> 00:47:32,640\r\nThe whole thing?\r\nCover to cover.\r\n\r\n746\r\n00:47:33,120 --> 00:47:36,397\r\nI've got excerpts. Analysis.\r\n3,000 words ready for editing.\r\n\r\n747\r\n00:47:38,480 --> 00:47:39,550\r\nYou start going over that.\r\n\r\n748\r\n00:47:40,120 --> 00:47:43,318\r\nGet graphics\r\nworking on tables, charts,\r\nthe whole nine yards.\r\n\r\n749\r\n00:47:44,160 --> 00:47:45,230\r\nJanine!\r\n\r\n750\r\n00:47:46,200 --> 00:47:47,759\r\nWhat's the angle, five words?\r\n\r\n751\r\n00:47:47,880 --> 00:47:49,360\r\nFar left of center.\r\n\r\n752\r\n00:47:49,440 --> 00:47:50,430\r\nThat's four.\r\n\r\n753\r\n00:47:50,520 --> 00:47:51,510\r\nVery far left of center.\r\n\r\n754\r\n00:47:51,600 --> 00:47:53,000\r\nEnough to put\r\nWalker on his heels?\r\n\r\n755\r\n00:47:53,080 --> 00:47:54,840\r\nFuck his heels.\r\nThis will put him on his ass.\r\n\r\n756\r\n00:47:55,440 --> 00:47:56,430\r\nWhat's up?\r\n\r\n757\r\n00:47:56,920 --> 00:47:59,560\r\nWe've got a copy\r\nof the administration's\r\neducation bill.\r\n\r\n758\r\n00:47:59,640 --> 00:48:01,120\r\nYou're going to\r\nwork with Zoe,\r\ndo background copy.\r\n\r\n759\r\n00:48:01,200 --> 00:48:02,793\r\nZoe Barnes?\r\nRight here.\r\n\r\n760\r\n00:48:03,680 --> 00:48:05,160\r\nWhatever she needs.\r\n\r\n761\r\n00:48:05,240 --> 00:48:06,196\r\nShouldn't I be writing the...\r\n\r\n762\r\n00:48:06,320 --> 00:48:07,310\r\nShe wrote it already.\r\n\r\n763\r\n00:48:07,400 --> 00:48:10,359\r\nAnd I want you to re-write\r\nit, then re-write it again.\r\nYou'll help her.\r\n\r\n764\r\n00:48:10,440 --> 00:48:13,160\r\nTom, I'm your chief\r\npolitical correspondent.\r\nGo.\r\n\r\n765\r\n00:48:13,240 --> 00:48:14,310\r\nI want this by tomorrow.\r\n\r\n766\r\n00:48:14,480 --> 00:48:15,550\r\nBut I need to focus\r\non the inauguration.\r\n\r\n767\r\n00:48:15,640 --> 00:48:16,915\r\nThis is more important.\r\n\r\n768\r\n00:48:17,480 --> 00:48:19,153\r\nLet's get started.\r\n\r\n769\r\n00:48:19,480 --> 00:48:21,200\r\n<i>That I will\r\nfaithfully execute the office</i>\r\n\r\n770\r\n00:48:21,320 --> 00:48:22,959\r\n<i>of President of\r\nthe United States.</i>\r\n\r\n771\r\n00:48:23,040 --> 00:48:25,555\r\n<i>\"...that I will faithfully\r\nexecute the office...\"</i>\r\n\r\n772\r\n00:48:25,640 --> 00:48:27,632\r\nPower is a lot\r\nlike real estate.\r\n\r\n773\r\n00:48:27,840 --> 00:48:29,832\r\nIt's all about location,\r\nlocation, location.\r\n\r\n774\r\n00:48:30,840 --> 00:48:32,559\r\nThe closer you\r\nare to the source,\r\n\r\n775\r\n00:48:32,680 --> 00:48:34,831\r\nthe higher your property value.\r\n\r\n776\r\n00:48:36,040 --> 00:48:38,430\r\nCenturies from now,\r\nwhen people\r\nwatch this footage,\r\n\r\n777\r\n00:48:39,000 --> 00:48:42,437\r\nwho will they see\r\nsmiling just at\r\nthe edge of the frame?\r\n\r\n778\r\n00:48:42,920 --> 00:48:44,479\r\n<i>\"So help me God.\"</i>\r\n\r\n779\r\n00:48:44,920 --> 00:48:46,149\r\n<i>Congratulations.</i>\r\n\r\n780\r\n00:49:02,800 --> 00:49:06,271\r\n<i>Today is not about\r\nthe next four years.</i>\r\n\r\n781\r\n00:49:07,680 --> 00:49:10,275\r\n<i>It's about\r\nthe next four decades.</i>\r\n\r\n782\r\n00:49:10,960 --> 00:49:13,520\r\n<i>You've placed your faith in me,</i>\r\n\r\n783\r\n00:49:13,600 --> 00:49:18,277\r\n<i>and I, in turn,\r\nchoose to place that\r\nfaith in our children.</i>\r\n\r\n784\r\n00:49:19,720 --> 00:49:24,317\r\n<i>Our children\r\nare the key to\r\nthis nation's future,</i>\r\n\r\n785\r\n00:49:24,880 --> 00:49:28,715\r\n<i>and that's why\r\nthe first order of business\r\nfor this administration</i>\r\n\r\n786\r\n00:49:28,800 --> 00:49:32,396\r\n<i>will be a comprehensive\r\neducation reform bill</i>\r\n\r\n787\r\n00:49:32,480 --> 00:49:38,556\r\n<i>to properly fix, finance\r\nand strengthen our\r\nnation's schools.</i>\r\n\r\n788\r\n00:49:42,600 --> 00:49:44,717\r\n<i>And I pledge to you,</i>\r\n\r\n789\r\n00:49:45,080 --> 00:49:48,152\r\n<i>we will have that bill\r\non the floor of the Congress</i>\r\n\r\n790\r\n00:49:48,240 --> 00:49:51,790\r\n<i>within the first 100 days\r\nof this administration.</i>\r\n\r\n791\r\n00:49:58,120 --> 00:50:00,237\r\nIt was so nice\r\nof you to make this possible.\r\n\r\n792\r\n00:50:00,400 --> 00:50:01,521\r\nWhen you called me, I was...\r\n\r\n793\r\n00:50:01,560 --> 00:50:02,516\r\nNot another word.\r\n\r\n794\r\n00:50:02,600 --> 00:50:06,071\r\nI'm going to miss\r\nout on my ultimate\r\nFrisbee league this season.\r\n\r\n795\r\n00:50:06,560 --> 00:50:07,960\r\nNo, I'm serious.\r\n\r\n796\r\n00:50:08,040 --> 00:50:10,077\r\nA few of us on Budget\r\nhave quite a rivalry\r\n\r\n797\r\n00:50:10,200 --> 00:50:12,237\r\ngoing with the guys on Finance.\r\n\r\n798\r\n00:50:12,360 --> 00:50:14,670\r\nIt's fierce.\r\nWe get physical.\r\n\r\n799\r\n00:50:14,760 --> 00:50:19,710\r\nAnybody gets between\r\nme and that goal line,\r\nI will take that sucker down.\r\n\r\n800\r\n00:50:39,920 --> 00:50:43,152\r\nDonald, I've been looking\r\nfor you everywhere, maestro.\r\n\r\n801\r\n00:50:43,240 --> 00:50:44,833\r\nYeah.\r\nLet me help\r\nyou out there.\r\n\r\n802\r\n00:50:45,000 --> 00:50:47,231\r\nI really like\r\nthe work you've done\r\non the new draft.\r\n\r\n803\r\n00:50:47,320 --> 00:50:49,755\r\nIt's a big step\r\nforward. We're going to\r\nmake history together.\r\n\r\n804\r\n00:50:49,840 --> 00:50:51,035\r\nThanks for your\r\nencouragement, Francis.\r\n\r\n805\r\n00:50:51,120 --> 00:50:53,157\r\nListen, I've got some\r\nideas about subsidies...\r\n\r\n806\r\n00:50:53,240 --> 00:50:55,835\r\nCatherine! Hold on to\r\nthat thought, Donald.\r\n\r\n807\r\n00:50:57,000 --> 00:50:59,640\r\nDon't you look stunning.\r\n\r\n808\r\n00:51:00,280 --> 00:51:01,520\r\nWe Southern girls clean up well\r\n\r\n809\r\n00:51:01,560 --> 00:51:04,155\r\nwhen we get out\r\nof our Daisy Dukes\r\nand into some Vera Wang.\r\n\r\n810\r\n00:51:04,240 --> 00:51:07,517\r\nAnd we Southern boys are\r\nslow with our words,\r\nbut we're fast on our feet.\r\n\r\n811\r\n00:51:07,600 --> 00:51:09,159\r\nMay I have the honor?\r\n\r\n812\r\n00:51:09,280 --> 00:51:10,794\r\nYou most certainly may.\r\n\r\n813\r\n00:51:36,440 --> 00:51:38,511\r\nMorning, Freddy.\r\nMornin', Frank.\r\n\r\n814\r\n00:51:38,600 --> 00:51:40,353\r\nHow's tricks?\r\nCan't kick.\r\n\r\n815\r\n00:51:41,200 --> 00:51:44,113\r\nYou want to go on in?\r\nNo, why don't you\r\nset me up outside?\r\n\r\n816\r\n00:51:44,200 --> 00:51:45,839\r\nOutside?\r\nIt's freezing out here.\r\n\r\n817\r\n00:51:45,920 --> 00:51:48,276\r\nWell, a little cold\r\nnever hurt anybody.\r\n\r\n818\r\n00:51:49,000 --> 00:51:50,070\r\nAnything you say, Frank.\r\n\r\n819\r\n00:51:50,960 --> 00:51:52,599\r\nIt'll be right up.\r\n\r\n820\r\n00:51:53,040 --> 00:51:56,431\r\nMy one guilty pleasure\r\nis a good rack of ribs.\r\nEven at 7:30 in the morning.\r\n\r\n821\r\n00:51:56,520 --> 00:51:57,840\r\nI have the whole\r\nplace to myself.\r\n\r\n822\r\n00:51:57,920 --> 00:51:59,991\r\nFreddy sometimes\r\nopens up just for me.\r\n\r\n823\r\n00:52:00,200 --> 00:52:02,192\r\nWhere I come from\r\nin South Carolina,\r\n\r\n824\r\n00:52:02,280 --> 00:52:04,590\r\npeople didn't have two\r\npennies to rub together.\r\n\r\n825\r\n00:52:04,880 --> 00:52:07,349\r\nA rack of ribs was\r\na luxury, like...\r\n\r\n826\r\n00:52:11,520 --> 00:52:13,591\r\nChristmas in July.\r\n\r\n827\r\n00:52:52,160 --> 00:52:53,879\r\nThis web traffic\r\nis absolutely crazy.\r\n\r\n828\r\n00:52:58,080 --> 00:53:01,391\r\n<i>Blue Camry's\r\nwanted in connection\r\nto a canine hit-and-run.</i>\r\n\r\n829\r\n00:53:01,480 --> 00:53:03,597\r\nHey, is this your car?\r\n\r\n830\r\n00:53:03,760 --> 00:53:05,877\r\nWhat's going on?\r\n\r\n831\r\n00:53:08,600 --> 00:53:10,239\r\nYou want seconds, Frank?\r\n\r\n832\r\n00:53:10,360 --> 00:53:11,999\r\nI better not.\r\n\r\n833\r\n00:53:13,960 --> 00:53:17,192\r\nTell you what, Freddy.\r\nYes, I will.\r\n\r\n834\r\n00:53:17,920 --> 00:53:19,912\r\nI'm feeling hungry today.\r\n\r\n9999\r\n00:00:0,500 --> 00:00:2,00\r\n<font color=\"#ffff00\" size=14>www.tvsubtitles.net</font>\r\n","markerStore":{"nextMarkerId":1,"markersById":{"0":{"range":{"start":{"row":0,"column":0},"end":{"row":0,"column":0}},"properties":{"type":"selection","editorId":576,"preserveFolds":true},"reversed":false,"tailed":false,"valid":true,"invalidate":"never","maintainHistory":true}},"version":2},"history":{"version":3,"nextCheckpointId":0,"undoStack":[],"redoStack":[]},"encoding":"utf8","filePath":"/Users/joegesualdo/Downloads/House of Cards US  - 1x01 - Chapter 1.HDTV.en.srt","digestWhenLastPersisted":"da39a3ee5e6b4b0d3255bfef95601890afd80709","preferredLineEnding":null,"deserializer":"TextBuffer","version":2},{"load":true,"text":"","markerStore":{"nextMarkerId":1680,"markersById":{"0":{"range":{"start":{"row"